{"tid":2069593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［係咪戇撚鳩］信報：‘民主派’（主要白鴿）認為統一口徑意義不大 因為恐怕全面出局","createTime":"2020-06-18T13:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T13:41:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"133367360bbee80814d941a690969cccfc448a44","tid":2069593,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:41:05.000Z","msg":"信報：<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯雖然民主派內部曾經有人提議，全體泛民回答選舉主任提問時一律統一口徑，以免官方「拉一派、打一派」，只DQ個別候選人，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可是很多泛民同路人認為此舉意義不大。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n首先，要求全數民主派參選人協商出一套各板塊皆接受的「標準答案」回應選舉主任提問，可說非常艱難，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就算成功，答案必然是「DQ風險極高」，屆時所有候選人恐怕「全部出局」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n也有民主派人士認為，近年選舉主任的DQ紅線難以捉摸，即使參選人回答DQ風險甚低的「標準答案」，選舉主任亦可翻查其過往的社交媒體紀錄，找出「不真誠擁護《基本法》」的證據，「佢要DQ你，實搵到原因」。⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2497372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2497372&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=21acadd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2497372</a><br />\n<br />\n假設哩段係真：<br />\n依家主要得番民主黨未簽聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定主要係你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共最理想既結局，唔係全部DQ，而係十零個泛民+十零個假黃中間派<br />\n<br />\n中共依家既策略<br />\n係推一堆扮黃中間派嚟<br />\n然後dq哂啲本土素人<br />\n俾老泛民攞十零廿席<br />\n另一堆偽黃攞十零廿席<br />\n<br />\n因為1/3係23.3席<br />\n老泛民係廿席以下<br />\n已經足夠安全而又保住議會一定&lsquo;民主成份&rsquo;，代表性<br />\n仲可以振振有詞咁講<br />\n只係dq&rsquo;一少撮人&lsquo;<br />\n<br />\n而做到趕盡殺絕攞哂70席，除咗過法案再快少少外冇著數<br />\n反而唔知香港又會唔會&rsquo;出大事&lsquo;，同俾更多彈藥俾外國制裁<br />\n唔好忘記9月選舉，11月美國大選<br />\n<br />\n就算澳門都留幾個反對派做疏氣孔<br />\n何況香港<br />\n<br />\n你聯署咗聲明<br />\n中共用份聲明嚟dq<br />\n就變咗要dq哂<br />\n<br />\n唔用份聲明嚟dq<br />\n即係份聲明合法<br />\n<br />\n唔用份聲明dq而仲想針對性咁dq素人<br />\n就要逐個夾硬砌故仔<br />\n做得核突好多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/不管-35-是否可能-初選亦必不可少/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%8D%E7%AE%A1-35-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD-%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%A6%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%91%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=d4080863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%8D%E7%AE%A1-35-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD-%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%A6%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%91%2F&h=dbaa319c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/不管-35-是否可能-初選亦必不可少/</a>"},{"pid":"e8ac8903454bee190f2de6535e294ee46d39db49","tid":2069593,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3005a81cc9a3fb3d166f282a7bd8076b332617d0","tid":2069593,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"8s"}]}